Autopus-ADK는 코딩 CLI에 하네스를 설치하는 Go 기반 셋업 도구입니다.

Usage:
  auto [command]

Available Commands:
  arch        Architecture analysis and enforcement
  check       Run harness rule checks
  completion  Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell
  docs        Lookup library documentation via Context7
  doctor      Check autopus harness health
  experiment  Run and manage experiment loops
  hash        Hash each line of a file using xxhash
  help        Help about any command
  init        Initialize autopus harness in the current project
  issue       Manage auto issue reports
  lore        Decision knowledge management via git trailers
  lsp         LSP-based code intelligence
  orchestra   다중 모델 오케스트레이션으로 코드를 분석한다
  platform    Manage platforms
  search      Search the web using Exa API (requires EXA_API_KEY)
  setup       Generate and manage project documentation for AI agents
  skill       Autopus 빌트인 스킬 관리
  spec        SPEC document management
  status      Show SPEC dashboard
  telemetry   Manage pipeline telemetry
  update      Update autopus harness files
  verify      Run frontend UX verification via Playwright screenshots
  version     Print version information

Flags:
      --config string   Config file path (default: ./autopus.yaml)
  -h, --help            help for auto
  -v, --verbose         Enable verbose output

Use "auto [command] --help" for more information about a command.
